intro: The Ambassador of the United States of America to the Russian Federation is the ambassador extraordinary and plenipotentiary from the United States of America to the Russian Federation. Jon Huntsman Jr. held the position from October 2017 until October 3, 2019. On December 12, 2019, the United States Senate confirmed John J. Sullivan as the next ambassador.
